channel.title: RuneScape-Radio MUST SEE!
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i344.photobucket.com/albums/p348/tekidder_2008/1.jpg[/img] Hey I made a website where I host a radio station that people can call and request songs or participate in 'random events ' and win prizes such as ipods, ipads, computers, psp, itouch, ps3, xbox360, xbox ps3 and psp games, runescape membership and so much more!
On RuneScape Radio we talk about Runescape, Jagex, likes, dislikes, Private Servers, websites, basically anything you can think about with runescape!
If you are interested in checking it out i can pm you the link! :)
Here is a vid: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=51kUcXtbYKU
RuneScape-Radio's goal is to be a station hosted on the FM radio! Help support our cause! The first broadcast is tomorrow (May 8th 2010) at 12pm-1pm pacific time. #5 caller will receive a new Alienware PC laptop! [b]Please comment[/b]
